{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see Reina right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went through the whole procedure of checking in, as they call it-- which is pretty awful, and dumb, at the same time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the worst was that, it not only took forever-- for no reason whatsoever-- but you had, then, also-- some of the stuff was that you had to undress completely.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ones who checked you for more than a hidden ring-- but for diamonds-- in like little cubicles, when you go to doctor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Men and women were not separated, which didn't matter anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had only one hanger to hang your clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you stood facing the wall in a knee-bent position, legs spread apart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these animals, those two horse-teeth looking Belgian guards, checked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whoever protested got the worst of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this is the first thing you learn-- you don't protest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You do it as fast as possible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Get in and out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had an old woman, and they truly, truly manhandled her to such a degree, it was pathetic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her husband wanted to get them away from her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They dragged her husband-- who held onto her leg and said, don't go with them, don't go with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the while I kept thinking, what about the nine-months-old baby?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are they going to do with the baby?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or with that elderly couple?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Are they going make her undress-- a lady, truly a lady?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And have her stand there, looking whether she had some hidden diamonds?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Awful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You went through about five or six or seven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you told them your name, and you told them your address.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was all stupid.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
